Reasoning: The paper deals with combinatorial and structural properties of palindromes in two-dimensional words, which are topics that fall under discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The study of palindromes also involves algorithms and data structures (cs.CC, cs.DS), as well as information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG) for pattern recognition.
